Very nice app considering the countless 'not so good photography apps' on the Store. Its nice to see a developer doing something serious for Android photography rather than yet another 'selfie' app. Android falls way behind Apple with photography apps and this is a move in the right direction. Good selection of filters, a little like a combination of VSCO/RNI Films but probably easier to navigate.  So far the only problem I've encountered is the image always loads upside down, not to sure why but its easy enough to rotate. Keep up the good work!
